workflow.name: Automated SEO keyword analysis with RapidAPI and Google Sheets
workflow.description:
## üöÄ Automated Keyword Analysis with On-Page SEO Workflow 

## üìå Description
Boost your SEO strategy by automating keyword research and on-page SEO analysis with n8n. This workflow uses user input (keyword + country), retrieves essential data using the powerful [**SEO On-Page API**](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/seo-on-page), and saves it directly into Google Sheets. Ideal for marketers, content strategists, and SEO agencies looking for efficiency.

---

## üîÅ Node-by-Node Flow explanation 
### 1. **üü¢ On form submission**
Triggers the workflow when a user submits a keyword and country via a simple form.

### 2. **üì¶ Global Storage**
Captures and stores the submitted keyword and country for use across the workflow.

### 3. **üåç Keyword Insights Request**
Sends a POST request to the [**SEO On-Page API**](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/seo-on-page) to fetch keyword suggestions (broad match keywords).

### 4. **üßæ Re-Format**
Extracts the relevant `broadMatchKeywords` array from the keyword API response.

### 5. **üìä Keyword Insights**
Appends extracted keyword suggestions into the **"Keyword Insights"** tab in Google Sheets.

### 6. **üìâ KeyWord Difficulty Request**
Sends a second POST request to the [**SEO On-Page API**](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/seo-on-page) to fetch keyword difficulty and SERP data.

### 7. **üìà Re-Format 2**
Extracts the `keywordDifficultyIndex` value from the API response.

### 8. **üìÑ KeyWord Difficulty**
Saves the keyword difficulty score into the **"KeyWord Difficulty"** sheet for reference.

### 9. **üîç Re -Format 5**
Extracts SERP result data from the difficulty API response.

### 10. **üóÇÔ∏è SERP Result**
Appends detailed SERP data into the **"Serp Analytics"** sheet in Google Sheets.

---

## üéØ Benefits

- ‚úÖ **Fully Automated SEO Research** ‚Äì No manual data entry or API calls required.
- üîÅ **Real-time Data Collection** ‚Äì Powered by [**SEO On-Page API on RapidAPI**](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/seo-on-page), ensuring fresh and reliable results.
- üìä **Organized Insights** ‚Äì Data is cleanly categorized into separate Google Sheets tabs.
- ‚è±Ô∏è **Time Saver** ‚Äì Instantly analyze keywords without switching between tools.

---

## üí° Use Cases

- üìå **SEO Agencies** ‚Äì Generate keyword reports for clients automatically.
- üìù **Content Writers** ‚Äì Discover keyword difficulty and SERP competition before drafting.
- üßë‚Äçüíª **Digital Marketers** ‚Äì Monitor keyword trends and search visibility in real-time.
- üìà **Bloggers & Influencers** ‚Äì Choose better keywords to rank faster on search engines.

---

## üîó API Reference

This workflow is powered by the **[SEO On-Page API](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/seo-on-page)** available on RapidAPI. It offers keyword research, difficulty metrics, and SERP analytics through simple endpoints, making it ideal for automation with n8n.

---

> ‚ö†Ô∏è **Note:** Make sure to replace `"your key"` with your actual RapidAPI key in both HTTP Request nodes for successful API calls.

Create your **free n8n account** and set up the workflow in just a few minutes using the link below:

parameters.content:
# üìä OnPage SEO (Keyword) - n8n Workflow

## üìù Description
This workflow automates keyword analysis for on-page SEO using form input (keyword and country), fetches keyword data from an API (including keyword insights, difficulty, and SERP data), and saves results into a Google Sheet.

---

## üîß Node-by-Node Overview

### 1. **On form submission**
Triggers when a form is submitted with required inputs: `keyword` and `country`.

### 2. **Global Storage**
Stores the form inputs (`keyword`, `country`) into the workflow context for further use.

### 3. **Keyword Insights Request**
Sends a POST request to the SEO API (`keyword-tool.php`) to fetch keyword data such as broad match keywords.

### 4. **KeyWord Difficulty Request**
Sends a POST request to the SEO API (`keywordDifficulty.php`) to retrieve keyword difficulty and SERP results.

### 5. **Re-Format**
Parses and extracts `broadMatchKeywords` from the keyword insights API response.

### 6. **Re-Format 2**
Parses and extracts the `keywordDifficultyIndex` from the difficulty API response.

### 7. **Re -Format 5**
Parses and extracts `serpResults` from the difficulty API response.

### 8. **Keyword Insights**
Appends the extracted keyword insights into the **"Keyword Insights"** sheet in the connected Google Sheet.

### 9. **KeyWord Difficulty**
Appends keyword and difficulty index data into the **"KeyWord Difficulty"** sheet in the connected Google Sheet.

### 10. **SERP Result**
Appends extracted SERP data into the **"Serp Analytics"** sheet in the connected Google Sheet.

---

### 1. üü¢ **On form submission**
**Type:** `formTrigger`  
**Description:** Triggers when a user submits the form with `keyword` and `country` fields.

### 2. üì¶ **Global Storage**
**Type:** `set`  
**Description:** Stores the keyword and country values from the form for use in later nodes.

### 3. üåê **Keyword Insights Request**
**Type:** `httpRequest`  
**Description:** Sends a POST request to the RapidAPI SEO endpoint (`keyword-tool.php`) to get broad match keyword insights.

### 4. üåê **KeyWord Difficulty Request**
**Type:** `httpRequest`  
**Description:** Sends a POST request to the RapidAPI SEO endpoint (`keywordDifficulty.php`) to get keyword difficulty and SERP data.

### 5. üßæ **Re-Format**
**Type:** `code`  
**Description:** Extracts the `broadMatchKeywords` array from the `keyword-tool` API response.

### 6. üìä **Keyword Insights**
**Type:** `googleSheets`  
**Description:** Appends the extracted broad match keyword data to the **"Keyword Insights"** sheet in Google Sheets.

### 7. üßÆ **Re-Format 2**
**Type:** `code`  
**Description:** Extracts the `keywordDifficultyIndex` from the `keywordDifficulty` API response.

### 8. üìà **KeyWord Difficulty**
**Type:** `googleSheets`  
**Description:** Appends the keyword and difficulty index to the **"KeyWord Difficulty"** sheet.

### 9. üóÇÔ∏è **Re -Format 5**
**Type:** `code`  
**Description:** Extracts the `serpResults` data from the `keywordDifficulty` API response.

### 10. üîç **SERP Result**
**Type:** `googleSheets`  
**Description:** Appends the extracted SERP analytics data to the **"Serp Analytics"** sheet.
